Alan Rickman: A life in pictures
Actor Alan Rickman, known for films including Harry Potter, Die Hard, Truly Madly Deeply and Robin Hood: Prince of Thieves,has died at the age of 69.A family statement said: "He was surrounded by family and friends."Here, we present pictures of him in some of his best known roles.